@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_lspwek(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.abs((v2 + 0.31 - tmp + 0.82)))
    v2 = ((wp.cos(v2 + 0.93) + (v0 + 0.75 - v0 + 0.12)) + v2)
    v0 = (0.27 * 0.33)
    v2 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
